      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 104.</p><p>Tier II: Combat Master</p><p>Prerequisite: Technique Student</p><p>Defensive Proficiency. While wielding a melee weapon, increase your AC by 3.</p><p>Greater Critical. Your critical range is increased by 1. When you score a critical hit, your attack ignores resistances to its damage type.</p><p>Perfected Saves. You gain proficiency in Strength, Dexterity, and Constitution saving throws.</p></div>",
